Package edu.umn.biomedicus.vocabulary

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TermIndexBuilder  
    Vocabulary
    Retrieves the system-wide term indexes used by BioMedICUS.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LabelWordIndexes
    Takes the text of words from parse tokens and labels their index value.
    RocksDbVocabStore
    Vocabulary store using RocksDB as the backend.
    RocksDbVocabularyBuilder  
    VocabularyInitializer
    Initializes the BioMedICUS vocabulary using the specialist lexicon and a UMLS installation
    VocabularyModule  
    VocabularySearchExprFactory
    Performs vocabulary substitution for SearchExprFactory. Looks for strings of the forms: $words"word", $terms"term", and $norms"norm" and replaces them with their respective string indices.
